            "reviewGeneral": {
              "raw": "{\"nodeType\":\"document\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"As a low rarity unit, Lee Dafoe does not have the stats necessary to meet the baseline requirements expected of him as a frontline tank.\\n\\nLee Dafoe does not possess relevant utility that would justify using him. There are no trade-offs within the kit that would compensate for the stat deficiency.\\n\\nFor all scenarios, there exist more effective alternatives for the role.\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}}]}]}"
