            "introduction": {
              "introduction": "　Lee Dafoe is a defender with excellent skills against multiple enemies. His right arm, covered by steel armor, was created from his Watch. He uses it as shield and weapon.\n\n　Lee was once an aspiring boxer, but he lost his right arm when he was jumped by gangsters. He awakened his powers as a Counter after the incident.\n　Although he lost his dream of becoming a boxer, he is now working at the Frontier with a new goal.　Lee is planning to build a hospital back home so that there will be no more victims like him. It doesn't matter that the Frontier is still a small-sized mercenary group. He dreamed of becoming a boxer even in a dark, moldy gym. Now that he has a new arm, he can do anything. "
